// Demo profile avatars: famous-person portraits, one per demo user.
// Each entry is a 256x256 JPEG (sourced from Wikimedia Commons, cropped/resized
// for this private demo) embedded as base64. The seed route decodes b64 with
// Buffer.from(b64, "base64") into the users.avatar BYTEA column (avatar_mime = mime).
// Keyed by EXACT demo username. Mapping (username -> person):
//   thefacebook_tom -> Steve Jobs
//   harvardhannah -> Marie Curie
//   djmarcus -> Bob Marley
//   priya_codes -> Ada Lovelace
//   skater_dave -> Tony Hawk
//   artsy_lena -> Frida Kahlo
//   coachrandy -> Pelé
//   bookish_mei -> Jane Austen
//   gamer_greg -> Keanu Reeves
//   rower_chad -> Michael Phelps
//   ivy_isabel -> Barack Obama
//   photog_nate -> Ansel Adams
//   a_capella_amy -> Freddie Mercury
//   frat_brett -> Will Ferrell
//   thesis_tariq -> Albert Einstein
//   premed_paula -> Rosalind Franklin
//   quad_quinn -> Julia Child

